  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a pressure cooker over medium heat. Add minced garlic and sauté until fragrant.",
    "Add vermicelli noodles to the pot with a pinch of salt, cook for about 3-4 minutes or according to package instructions.",
    "Pour in heavy cream mixture (half-and-half + heavy whipping cream), Parmesan cheese, and stir well. Let it simmer on low heat.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley leaves if desired and serve immediately."
